{"tid":1499382,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日國泰，聽日係你公司。呢單野係煲得大。","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T15:10:30.000Z","uid":141597,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"20db9895e87a8602fa2ac4062af657366ebcdf71","tid":1499382,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:38:14.000Z","msg":"我覺得要煲大佢。<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，而家有咩公司唔係狂同大陸做生意。國泰而家係咁鳩炒，他日所有外資都一樣會受壓，你份工都笈笈可危。<br />\n<br />\n航空業一定要幫手，有邊間airline唔駛飛大陸空域，今日落得呢條order，講得難聽啲，大陸要壟斷成個空域唔係無可能。<br />\n<br />\n國泰人我諗一定要搞罷工，我唔撚信你炒晒成間公司，點罷點談判，台灣嘅案例應該夠晒做，問心唔會有人會想喺一間會限制自己嘅私人言論自由嘅公司做，仲要唔影響公司業務。<br />\n<br />\n大家有無諗法"},{"pid":"4c326ec0f95f1defde28ed29103049c9fbbbf7be","tid":1499382,"uid":141597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"推，我唔係cx做，但有frd係，完全feel到嗰種傍徨"},{"pid":"5bcba62e593cc5bad20d10fd62c4d8479b64020e","tid":1499382,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:39:42.000Z","msg":"我自己都係外資，但都係日日講普通話"},{"pid":"bd32ec0af1dd3402b9a04f51665a6e8c6568c83b","tid":1499382,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bcecc70ca5eadb79708a7d60a5a0668aed6baeab","tid":1499382,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e5e1c2b3da612ac890cd81d98cd624c762b1fd53","tid":1499382,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:43:56.000Z","msg":"國泰已成活死人，不如引刀成一快<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1499235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1499235</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n第12攻，攬炒Channel 上線！連環去信英國外相、商會，支援Simon、國泰員工、HSBC！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1498555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1498555</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"53a22f6e490262565ea9148af14db34a985a3967","tid":1499382,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT